# API Contracts, OpenAPI, SDK Regeneration

> This rule is the source of truth for Cursor agent behaviour. Templates and commands are supporting references.

## When API Changes

If API behaviour, endpoints, DTOs, or annotations change:

- Update the OpenAPI spec (`docs/mapi/openapi.yaml`)
- Regenerate the SDK/clients as required
- Add or update contract/API tests covering the change (success + error paths)

